  • Description: During switching operations in the Superior Yard a crew reported an odor. Upon inspection by the local BNSF Mechanical responder, a leak from the manway of GATX 90658 was determined to be the source of the odor. One of the BNSF Hazmat Response contractors was called out to install a manway gasket, clean and secure the car for release to destination.
